title: Aleksandr Korotayev
text:
Aleksandr Stanislavovich Korotayev (; born 15 July 1992) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Olimp-Dolgoprudny">FC Olimp-Dolgoprudny</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Rotor%20Volgograd">FC Rotor Volgograd</a> on 11 March 2013 in a game against <a href="FC%20Neftekhimik%20Nizhnekamsk">FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk</a>.
